.title Help: Graphics Utilities Package
ABOUT THIS PACKAGE
The Graphics Utilities package contains the X Windows System(TM)
and other utilities which provide a fast, high-resolution
graphics subsystem for the Desktop Manager.This package also
allows you to run distributed X Windows applications on remote
systems using your local system's keyboard and display.

If you install this package, you must also install the
Networking Support Utilities package.

EXITING THE PACKAGE SELECTION MENU
Press <Enter> to enter your selections and to return to the
Install Menu.
                                    (CONTINUED)
.page
EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Package Selection menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
